.TH SLLISTENIPV4SOCKET 3 "2026-05-15" "silverlib v1.4.1" "silverlib manual"
.SH NAME
SLListenIPv4Socket - Prepares socket for incoming connections
.SH LIBRARY
silverlib library
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #define SILVER_LIB_IMPLEMENTATION
.B #include "silverlib.h"

.BI "int SLListenIPv4Socket(ListeningContext" " *ctx" ")"
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Function wrapper of \fBbind\fP(3), \fBlisten\fP(3) and
\fBconnect\fP(3) it binds the socket into a specific
address and port, sets it on listening mode, and waits
for a connection\.
.SH RETURN VALUE
Upon successful completion shall return a non-negative
number reprecentating the file descriptor of the accepted
socket\. Otherwise, a value of -1 shall be returned\.
